name: Ludmilla El Golilla - Retro round "teashades" Vers.
description:
Ludmilla is a primate that loves to change look and to get crazy when the music hits! This is the 4# NFT of a ongoing collection!
With it we want to raise awareness for the beauty of different characters and styles we have on this loco planet!

This version inspired by the legendary teashades-sunglasses were a popular choice for pop icons in the 1960s and 70s.

3D Sculpting | Rendering | Hair Simulation | mp4 loop 1280x1280px | SELFMADE MUSIC


Visual Artist - sirgulliver.art
